			<description><![CDATA[<p>
	Can your creativity and design captivate and delight users? Are your creations stunningly delightful, and yet clean and simple? Are you passionate about creating the most awesome user experiences that involve a blend of user friendly interactions and creative visual designs? If the answer is yes, then this job is for you!</p>
<p>
	As a Sr. Visual Designer at MindTickle, you will be responsible for creating the UIs of highly engaging gamification products for web and mobile applications. At MindTickle, we are creating cutting edge Saas products for the next generation employees. This is an unique opportunity to apply your design skills to transform mundane and cognitively demanding activities into delightful experiences.</p>
<p>
	<strong>Job Profile</strong></p>
<ul>
	<li>
		Converting wireframes and low fidelity protypes to high-fidelity UIs ready for development.</li>
	<li>
		Visualize and create high quality interfaces for complex game scenarios and interactions.</li>
	<li>
		Maintain high standards of aesthetics and usability in all the products.</li>
	<li>
		Enthusiasm to explore different mediums like mobile and pads.</li>
</ul>
<p>
	<strong>What are you expecting? &ndash; </strong><em>We will make you an offer you cannot refuse!</em></p>
<ul>
	<li>
		CTC will be market competitive and significant chunk of the stock options to make you rich.</li>
	<li>
		A cosy office set-up that will make you feel like at home.</li>
	<li>
		A Cultural Activity team responsible for packing our calendar with fun events, parties and trip.</li>
	<li>
		Catered lunches and a kitchen exploding with every possible food, snack, or coolers you can imagine.&nbsp;Craving something special? Then just add it to the list, and we&rsquo;ll stock it for you!</li>
	<li>
		A Sports Club &ndash; Balewadi stadium , which is around 1 kms from the office. You can have fun whatever sport activity you would want</li>
</ul>
<p>
	<strong>Required Qualifications/Skills</strong></p>
<ol>
	<li>
		BFA/MFA/B.Des/M.Des/B.Tech/BCA from prestigious Art/Design/Engineering colleges.</li>
	<li>
		Can design high quality creative, elegant and user-friendly Web 2.0 UIs and Mobile UIs.</li>
	<li>
		Has in-depth knowledge of icon designs, typogaphy, color theory and visual communication design.</li>
	<li>
		Proficient with Illustrator, Photoshop, Flash and similar softwares.</li>
	<li>
		Understands basic principle of usability and interaction design.</li>
	<li>
		2-5 years industry experience would be preferred but not required.</li>
</ol>
<p>
	<strong>Good to Have Skills</strong></p>
<ol>
	<li>
		Knowledge of animation and game design</li>
	<li>
		Knowledge of HTML and CSS</li>
</ol>
